6
00:01:10.499 --> 00:01:11.499
Yes.

7
00:01:13.070 --> 00:01:14.740
What are you doing here?

8
00:01:17.840 --> 00:01:20.510
I was just passing by.

9
00:01:37.559 --> 00:01:38.590
I see.

10
00:01:40.329 --> 00:01:42.430
