11
00:01:43.829 --> 00:01:45.329
Okay.

12
00:01:51.639 --> 00:01:53.570
Let's grab tea sometime.

13
00:01:54.439 --> 00:01:58.010
I'm a little frazzled right now.

14
00:02:03.049 --> 00:02:04.850
Sure. Let's do that.

15
00:02:40.719 --> 00:02:42.390
Are you all right?

16
00:02:42.559 --> 00:02:44.390
Did you go to the washroom?

17
00:02:44.789 --> 00:02:47.400
Yes. What about you?

18
00:02:48.129 --> 00:02:49.930
Are you feeling all right?

19
00:02:53.700 --> 00:02:56.270
I'm completely sober now.

20
00:02:59.640 --> 00:03:01.710
I had fun tonight.

21
00:03:02.640 --> 00:03:03.840
I'll get going.

22
00:03:04.550 --> 00:03:06.210
I'll drive you to your place.

23
00:03:06.779 --> 00:03:08.150
It's very close from here.

24
00:03:08.849 --> 00:03:11.289
I'm going to walk so I can get sober.

25
00:03:13.150 --> 00:03:15.390
Is your husband coming to get you?

26
00:03:16.219 --> 00:03:17.830
I was a little slow.

27
00:03:22.759 --> 00:03:24.930
Take care, then.

28
00:03:31.670 --> 00:03:33.809
(Ko Jung Min)

29
00:03:41.279 --> 00:03:43.479
(Wife)

30
00:03:45.520 --> 00:03:46.650
Hello?

31
00:03:47.360 --> 00:03:49.490
Ji Ho. Where are you?

32
00:03:50.629 --> 00:03:51.830
Here.

33
00:03:52.860 --> 00:03:53.930
Pardon?

34
00:04:02.939 --> 00:04:04.710
Why didn't you pick up...

35
00:04:06.670 --> 00:04:07.909
your phone?

36
00:04:09.379 --> 00:04:11.580
I didn't have a chance.

37
00:04:12.779 --> 00:04:14.950
I'm sorry. I was going to call.

38
00:04:19.590 --> 00:04:20.820
Let's go in.

39
00:04:57.830 --> 00:05:00.159
For some reason, I could drink a lot today.

40
00:05:01.060 --> 00:05:03.000
Maybe it's because I haven't drunk in a while.

41
00:05:03.700 --> 00:05:04.869
I see.

42
00:05:06.169 --> 00:05:07.799
Did you drink...

43
00:05:08.500 --> 00:05:10.239
with the production company?

44
00:05:12.909 --> 00:05:14.010
Yes.

45
00:05:14.979 --> 00:05:18.409
The CEO is a good drinker too.

46
00:05:20.919 --> 00:05:24.619
Drink this instead of cold water. Or you'll be sick tomorrow.

47
00:05:27.359 --> 00:05:30.460
Keep this by your bedside tonight.

48
00:05:30.789 --> 00:05:33.159
You might wake up feeling sick in the middle of the night.

49
00:05:40.330 --> 00:05:41.570
It's warm.

50
00:05:43.500 --> 00:05:44.739
Thank you.

51
00:05:58.849 --> 00:06:00.020
Goodnight.

52
00:06:01.760 --> 00:06:02.789
Goodnight.

53
00:06:04.659 --> 00:06:05.659
Ji Ho.

54
00:06:06.859 --> 00:06:07.929
Yes?

55
00:06:08.529 --> 00:06:09.760
Do you...

56
00:06:11.929 --> 00:06:13.630
want to sleep together again tonight?

57
00:06:16.940 --> 00:06:19.310
No, tonight's a little...

58
00:06:21.010 --> 00:06:22.140
I see.

59
00:06:23.580 --> 00:06:24.750
I'm sorry.

60
00:06:26.250 --> 00:06:28.580
No, it's not like that.

61
00:06:30.619 --> 00:06:32.320
I'm just a little tired.

62
00:06:33.119 --> 00:06:36.820
I snore more on days like this.

63
00:06:39.429 --> 00:06:40.529
I understand.

64
00:06:41.429 --> 00:06:44.700
I'll make more tea, so have it if you need to.

65
00:06:45.869 --> 00:06:46.929
Okay.

66
00:07:08.760 --> 00:07:11.029
I was engaged once.

67
00:07:11.289 --> 00:07:14.159
I was almost married once.

68
00:07:15.830 --> 00:07:18.299
The only things I can handle in life,

69
00:07:18.369 --> 00:07:21.039
are this house, Kitty, and myself.

70
00:07:21.070 --> 00:07:23.500
We were dating, and I got pregnant with his baby.

71
00:07:24.909 --> 00:07:27.039
Marriage isn't about just the couple.

72
00:07:27.210 --> 00:07:30.140
More than their feelings, it's a system that relies...

73
00:07:30.239 --> 00:07:31.549
more on the understanding of the surrounding people.

74
00:07:31.580 --> 00:07:34.950
I miscarried my baby and we broke up.

75
00:07:34.979 --> 00:07:36.919
His family was against our relationship too.

76
00:07:36.919 --> 00:07:39.549
I just wish...

77
00:07:40.150 --> 00:07:42.690
nothing would happen in my life.

78
00:08:03.239 --> 00:08:05.250
(Ko Jung Min)

79
00:08:07.450 --> 00:08:09.919
Some production company's CEO came to talk to me.

80
00:08:10.279 --> 00:08:12.950
She wasn't ordinary.

81
00:08:13.190 --> 00:08:15.820
She was strong...

82
00:08:15.820 --> 00:08:18.760
in a way that she doesn't hurt others but...

83
00:08:18.929 --> 00:08:20.630
protects instead.

84
00:08:22.599 --> 00:08:24.529
She's kind of like a tree.

85
00:08:40.479 --> 00:08:41.649
Hello?

86
00:08:42.719 --> 00:08:43.820
It's me.

87
00:08:45.149 --> 00:08:47.719
Yes. I know.

88
00:08:48.359 --> 00:08:51.359
I'm sorry to call when it's late.

89
00:08:52.060 --> 00:08:53.560
There is something I should tell you.

90
00:08:55.259 --> 00:08:56.359
Okay.

91
00:08:56.830 --> 00:08:58.629
Congratulations on getting the chance...

92
00:09:00.200 --> 00:09:01.300
to write again.

93
00:09:04.070 --> 00:09:07.310
This man is torn.

94
00:09:09.040 --> 00:09:11.580
I'm so glad...

95
00:09:13.550 --> 00:09:15.920
He's afraid.

96
00:09:17.320 --> 00:09:20.420
you're starting over again.

97
00:09:22.259 --> 00:09:23.920
He's nervous.

98
00:09:26.629 --> 00:09:27.859
Thank you.

99
00:09:30.969 --> 00:09:33.399
Sleep well, Ji Ho.

100
00:09:35.499 --> 00:09:36.599
Okay.

101
00:09:38.109 --> 00:09:39.440
You too.

102
00:09:46.580 --> 00:09:50.149
(Episode 14: Because This Is My First Confession)

103
00:09:51.820 --> 00:09:53.719
Should I just cut it like usual?

104
00:09:56.290 --> 00:09:57.389
No.

105
00:10:12.540 --> 00:10:13.769
Are you here?

106
00:10:17.310 --> 00:10:20.050
I'm sorry I contacted you out of the blue. I know you're busy.

107
00:10:20.149 --> 00:10:22.879
The CEO isn't busy.

108
00:10:23.080 --> 00:10:24.590
My employees are the ones that are busy.

109
00:10:26.219 --> 00:10:28.920
Wow, Ho Rang. You got a cut.

110
00:10:30.960 --> 00:10:33.759
Yes. I needed a change of scenery.

111
00:10:34.660 --> 00:10:37.330
It looks really good on you.

112
00:10:43.969 --> 00:10:45.239
Won Seok...

113
00:10:46.609 --> 00:10:48.479
really means it, right?

114
00:10:52.810 --> 00:10:54.119
Please, tell me.

115
00:10:54.680 --> 00:10:58.619
I want to get myself sorted out,

116
00:10:59.290 --> 00:11:03.160
but I didn't have anyone else to ask.

117
00:11:06.560 --> 00:11:09.229
He means it, right?

118
00:11:11.070 --> 00:11:12.369
For now,

119
00:11:13.969 --> 00:11:15.700
yes. I think so.

120
00:11:18.239 --> 00:11:19.340
Then...

121
00:11:20.609 --> 00:11:22.139
Even if I beg him,

122
00:11:23.580 --> 00:11:25.979
he won't come back to me. Right?

123
00:11:31.489 --> 00:11:32.749
Won Seok...

124
00:11:33.889 --> 00:11:38.090
seems to think that he's making you unhappy.

125
00:11:39.660 --> 00:11:43.160
That's why he decided to let you go.

126
00:11:46.800 --> 00:11:50.040
It's not because he wants to let go?

127
00:11:52.109 --> 00:11:53.639
I'm not sure,

128
00:11:55.410 --> 00:11:58.950
but if one thinks they're making their loved ones suffer,

129
00:12:00.410 --> 00:12:03.219
it makes them hate themselves.

130
00:12:04.290 --> 00:12:05.590
It feels miserable too.

131
00:12:07.859 --> 00:12:08.960
Okay.

132
00:12:10.359 --> 00:12:13.729
This is just where it ends for us.

133
00:12:19.629 --> 00:12:20.769
Sir.

134
00:12:22.639 --> 00:12:24.109
- Mr. Shin. - Hello.

135
00:12:24.109 --> 00:12:25.440
- Have you been well? - Yes.

136
00:12:25.440 --> 00:12:27.310
- Are you dropping by the office? - Yes.

137
00:12:27.540 --> 00:12:30.180
I had a financial consultation meeting.

138
00:12:33.749 --> 00:12:35.580
Aren't you going to introduce me?

139
00:12:36.519 --> 00:12:39.389
Could she be your...

140
00:12:39.389 --> 00:12:40.590
No, no.

141
00:12:40.590 --> 00:12:44.690
She's a close friend's non-girlfriend.

142
00:12:44.989 --> 00:12:47.560
She's my girlfriend's best friend.

143
00:12:47.560 --> 00:12:49.530
Ho Rang. Yang Ho Rang.

144
00:12:50.969 --> 00:12:54.399
Your girlfriend's best friend?

145
00:12:55.570 --> 00:12:56.670
Hello.

146
00:12:57.200 --> 00:13:01.080
My name is Shin Young Pyo. I take care of his business finances.

147
00:13:01.310 --> 00:13:04.649
I see. I don't have a business card.

148
00:13:05.810 --> 00:13:07.349
I'll get going.

149
00:13:07.649 --> 00:13:09.379
Okay, Ho Rang.

150
00:13:10.420 --> 00:13:12.249
I'll be in touch. Take care.

151
00:13:12.249 --> 00:13:13.349
Okay.

152
00:13:14.619 --> 00:13:15.759
Okay.

153
00:13:40.080 --> 00:13:42.820
Mr. Ma told me you're going to Sillim-dong.

154
00:13:44.090 --> 00:13:45.550
- Yes. - I'll give you a ride.

155
00:13:45.550 --> 00:13:47.119
The buses here run very infrequently.

156
00:13:47.960 --> 00:13:50.119
No, it's okay.

157
00:13:50.119 --> 00:13:51.889
I'm not a bad guy.

158
00:13:51.889 --> 00:13:54.129
I've known Mr. Ma for a long time.

159
00:13:59.129 --> 00:14:00.570
Do you live around there?

160
00:14:02.869 --> 00:14:04.369
No.

161
00:14:05.710 --> 00:14:07.910
I just have to pick up some stuff.

162
00:14:08.540 --> 00:14:09.680
I see.

163
00:14:10.879 --> 00:14:14.479
Ho Rang, do you really not know who I am?

164
00:14:15.749 --> 00:14:16.849
Pardon?

165
00:14:16.950 --> 00:14:18.149
I want to get married.

166
00:14:18.619 --> 00:14:19.690
What?

167
00:14:20.889 --> 00:14:23.259
"Dating Instead of Marriage". We chatted before...

168
00:14:23.259 --> 00:14:24.790
because you accepted my request.

169
00:14:27.830 --> 00:14:30.160
I was actually really surprised earlier.

170
00:14:30.259 --> 00:14:32.800
I recognized you right away.

171
00:14:34.399 --> 00:14:35.499
I see.

172
00:14:35.800 --> 00:14:39.440
You were the first person I talked to when I got the app.

173
00:14:40.310 --> 00:14:42.479
But you wouldn't reply after that one time.

174
00:14:42.940 --> 00:14:46.609
I figured that you dumped me.

175
00:14:48.420 --> 00:14:49.580
Well...

176
00:14:51.519 --> 00:14:54.590
I had just downloaded the app then,

177
00:14:54.590 --> 00:14:56.820
so I replied without thinking.

178
00:14:57.560 --> 00:14:59.359
It's Mr. Ma's app, so...

179
00:15:00.560 --> 00:15:04.070
Are you trying to draw a line between us?

180
00:15:05.830 --> 00:15:07.129
- What? - What is this?

181
00:15:07.469 --> 00:15:09.969
Are you surprised because I caught on?

182
00:15:10.070 --> 00:15:12.139
You can't deny it, can you?

183
00:15:22.320 --> 00:15:24.849
Thank you for the ride. Take care.

184
00:15:24.849 --> 00:15:25.950
Okay...

185
00:15:28.859 --> 00:15:30.119
Take care.

