00:16:46.999 --> 00:16:51.239
(I love you, honey! I love you, Ho Rang!)

193
00:17:32.849 --> 00:17:34.080
You were right.

194
00:17:35.149 --> 00:17:37.949
I'll become more honest...

195
00:17:39.220 --> 00:17:40.619
to my feelings.

196
00:17:51.699 --> 00:17:53.070
Why are you...

197
00:17:54.040 --> 00:17:55.300
Didn't you leave?

198
00:17:55.369 --> 00:17:58.970
You said you had luggage to pick up, and I thought it'd be heavy.

199
00:17:59.169 --> 00:18:01.580
You seemed to be in a bad condition too.

200
00:18:02.240 --> 00:18:03.379
What?

201
00:18:03.949 --> 00:18:06.679
- I'll give you a ride home. - No.

202
00:18:07.280 --> 00:18:09.980
You're making me uncomfortable.

203
00:18:10.149 --> 00:18:13.090
You're going to have a bad flu for certain.

204
00:18:13.649 --> 00:18:16.689
From whichever side I look at you, you're definitely having a flu.

205
00:18:17.429 --> 00:18:18.459
What?

206
00:18:19.760 --> 00:18:21.959
I mean, you look like you're about to faint.

207
00:18:22.459 --> 00:18:24.899
So how can I turn a blind eye?

208
00:18:29.540 --> 00:18:30.869
Give it to me.

209
00:18:34.379 --> 00:18:36.379
Shall I?

210
00:19:08.909 --> 00:19:12.280
We'll file a lawsuit following this process.

211
00:19:12.810 --> 00:19:15.419
As they go through an investigation, you'll have to...

212
00:19:15.419 --> 00:19:17.349
be questioned as a victim.

213
00:19:18.889 --> 00:19:20.790
Are you okay with it?

214
00:19:22.119 --> 00:19:25.090
Yes, I'm aware of it.

215
00:19:26.959 --> 00:19:30.000
Fortunately, you have the text messages and call history...

216
00:19:30.000 --> 00:19:32.470
to prove your claim against him.

217
00:19:33.399 --> 00:19:36.340
But if they start using media and news articles,

218
00:19:36.540 --> 00:19:38.010
things might get a bit messy.

219
00:19:38.240 --> 00:19:40.340
This matter is about the broadcasting industry after all.

220
00:19:42.310 --> 00:19:45.379
Yes, I'll have to brace myself for that.

221
00:19:46.810 --> 00:19:49.349
Okay, then we'll proceed accordingly.

222
00:19:51.020 --> 00:19:52.320
Oh, and...

223
00:19:54.060 --> 00:19:56.320
This is our contract.

224
00:19:56.320 --> 00:19:57.530
(Writing Contract)

225
00:20:00.359 --> 00:20:02.459
You don't have to sign it right now.

226
00:20:02.459 --> 00:20:04.699
Take it and read it carefully.

227
00:20:04.699 --> 00:20:07.300
Tell me if you want any changes.

228
00:20:11.810 --> 00:20:13.669
