248
00:21:26.709 --> 00:21:27.980
Ms. Ko.

249
00:21:28.250 --> 00:21:29.419
Yes?

250
00:21:29.750 --> 00:21:31.119
Shall we...

251
00:21:32.689 --> 00:21:34.320
