262
00:22:35.480 --> 00:22:37.520
Did your husband make it for you?

263
00:22:40.189 --> 00:22:41.189
Yes.

264
00:22:42.290 --> 00:22:43.590
My husband...

265
00:22:46.830 --> 00:22:48.099
made it for me.

266
00:22:58.540 --> 00:23:01.980
Before I sign the contract, I want to ask you about something.

267
00:23:08.020 --> 00:23:10.119
Okay, Ms. Yoon.

268
00:23:10.119 --> 00:23:12.820
It's about the man you talked about before.

269
00:23:14.919 --> 00:23:16.889
The man you almost got married with.

270
00:23:20.899 --> 00:23:22.000
Yes.

271
00:23:24.099 --> 00:23:25.669
What would you feel...

272
00:23:27.840 --> 00:23:29.500
if you ran into him again?

273
00:23:33.270 --> 00:23:34.780
Do you think...

274
00:23:36.010 --> 00:23:37.240
you'd love him...

275
00:23:39.580 --> 00:23:41.149
if you met him again?

276
00:23:45.649 --> 00:23:46.820
This...

277
00:23:47.889 --> 00:23:50.790
is related to our contract?

278
00:23:50.990 --> 00:23:52.060
Yes.

279
00:23:53.060 --> 00:23:54.699
It's related to our contract,

280
00:23:55.800 --> 00:23:57.500
and it's very important.

